---
title: Butternut & Cannellini Gratin with Lemony Garlic Greens
description: 'Gratin' is the French term for a baked dish with a crispy topping, usually made from breadcrumbs, cheese or a mixture of the two. So Frenchy, so delicious! The star of our gratin is butternut pumpkin, with its sweet roasted flesh wrapped up in a thick and creamy sauce. For the topping, we've combined herbed ciabatta and Parmesan – you’re in for a real treat!
